<i>(Regan) I think to go</i>

1127
01:11:33,623 --> 01:11:35,796
<i>from being the outcast

1128
01:11:35,875 --> 01:11:40,847
to being, uh, who he really was.

1129
01:11:40,838 --> 01:11:46,265
Because it was as though it was him
