01:20:20,441 --> 01:20:23,615
<i>we could not have imagined
how much our lives were gonna change</i>

1256
01:20:23,610 --> 01:20:25,283
<i>after that phone call.</i>

1257
01:20:25,279 --> 01:20:27,281
<i>Eva came on tour with Rodriguez</i>

1258
01:20:27,406 --> 01:20:30,080
<i>and the organizers arranged
